OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJohn Lewis will always be  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fowned by staff, says boss  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The boss of John Lewis has said the    
OL,6, company will always be owned by its    
OL,7, staff, "no ifs, no buts" as employees  
OL,8, backed her in a vote of confidence.    
OL,10,FDame Sharon White ruled out selling a  
OL,11,Fstake in the business, but said the    
OL,12,Fboard could consider external          
OL,13,Finvestment in future if it was needed. 
OL,15,FShe previously was understood to be    
OL,16,Fconsidering a change to its            
OL,17,Femployee-owned structure after over    
OL,18,F70-years.                              
OL,20,FBut the move sparked anger from staff, 
OL,21,Fwho currently fully own the retailer.  
